<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وتمتد حتى نهاية الآية <span class="c2">(١٨)</span> وهذه هي:<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>[سورة النجم <span class="c2">(٥٣)</span>: الآيات ١ الى ١٨]<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَالنَّجْمِ إِذا هَوى <span class="c2">(١)</span> ما ضَلَّ صاحِبُكُمْ وَما غَوى <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَما يَنْطِقُ عَنِ الْهَوى <span class="c2">(٣)</span> إِنْ هُوَ إِلاَّ وَحْيٌ يُوحى <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عَلَّمَهُ شَدِيدُ الْقُوى <span class="c2">(٥)</span> ذُو مِرَّةٍ فَاسْتَوى <span class="c2">(٦)</span> وَهُوَ بِالْأُفُقِ الْأَعْلى <span class="c2">(٧)</span> ثُمَّ دَنا فَتَدَلَّى <span class="c2">(٨)</span> فَكانَ قابَ قَوْسَيْنِ أَوْ أَدْنى <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَأَوْحى إِلى عَبْدِهِ ما أَوْحى <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ما كَذَبَ الْفُؤادُ ما رَأى <span class="c2">(١١)</span> أَفَتُمارُونَهُ عَلى ما يَرى <span class="c2">(١٢)</span> وَلَقَدْ رَآهُ نَزْلَةً أُخْرى <span class="c2">(١٣)</span> عِنْدَ سِدْرَةِ الْمُنْتَهى <span class="c2">(١٤)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عِنْدَها جَنَّةُ الْمَأْوى <span class="c2">(١٥)</span> إِذْ يَغْشَى السِّدْرَةَ ما يَغْشى <span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ما زاغَ الْبَصَرُ وَما طَغى <span class="c2">(١٧)</span> لَقَدْ رَأى مِنْ آياتِ رَبِّهِ الْكُبْرى <span class="c2">(١٨)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>